  "detailed_description": "<strong>Exanimate</strong> is a 2D pixel-art side scrolling platforming shooter where a players' instinct and will to survive is put to the ultimate test...<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENTER THE ZEDS</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/7265c2be6a7e0e61532cab0326a091ab.poster.avif?t=1740758367\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/7265c2be6a7e0e61532cab0326a091ab.webm?t=1740758367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/7265c2be6a7e0e61532cab0326a091ab.mp4?t=1740758367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>How long can you last before you give up and run?<br><br>The hordes of Zeds keep coming and coming and coming...<br><br>Do you hold your ground and battle to the bitter end?<br><br>Upgrade you weapons and manage your defences at the shop and continue the fight?<br><br>Or...<br><br>Do you run as soon as possible before their numbers overwhelm you and your friends?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >END TRANSMISSION</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/488948f3efa01a910ce16cae35bef70a.poster.avif?t=1740758367\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/488948f3efa01a910ce16cae35bef70a.webm?t=1740758367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/488948f3efa01a910ce16cae35bef70a.mp4?t=1740758367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Zombie Horde Destruction!</h2><br>Fight against over <strong>20</strong> different vicious zombies and learn how to efficiently dispatch each variation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4-player Mayhem!</h2><br>Same screen local co-op to ease the pain! Or does it?!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fully Stocked Shop!</h2><br>Power yourself every step of the way! Purchase new and unique weapons, buffs, barricades, turrets and more during  the heat of the fight!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bop your head while you explode those zeds!</h2><br>Enjoy killing the endless onslaught to a retro-style sound track!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/bd27f0b191b1bd4d3377f2886ff4218d.poster.avif?t=1740758367\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/bd27f0b191b1bd4d3377f2886ff4218d.webm?t=1740758367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806050/extras/bd27f0b191b1bd4d3377f2886ff4218d.mp4?t=1740758367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
